# Anti-Patterns

- ❌ Never let components exceed 200 lines
- ❌ Never add backend dependencies for card features
- ❌ Never use CSS variables as Framer Motion key values
- ❌ Never hardcode OG tags in client components
- ❌ Never try to hide web elements for print — use dedicated print container
- ❌ Never add animations that require JavaScript when CSS can do it
- ❌ Never use overflow:hidden on ancestors of sticky elements
- ✅ Always run npm run build after changes
- ✅ Always use @media print with @page { size: 3.5in 2in; margin: 0; }
- ✅ Always test on Samsung Internet for mobile features
